    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SubmitButton

    public class Button
extends AbstractToggleButton
    Button based on <button> element with different types and sizes.

    UiBinder example

     <b:Button type="PRIMARY">Save</b:Button>
     <b:Button type="DANGER">Delete</b:Button>
     <b:Button type="INFO" block="true>I'm a block level button</b:Button>
    Author:
    Sven Jacobs
    See Also:
    AbstractToggleButton, SubmitButton
